@startuml
title AI Asset Management - High-Level Component UML
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
left to right direction

actor "User" as User
component "Web Frontend\n(React/TypeScript)" as Frontend
component "Backend API\n(FastAPI)" as API
component "Identity & Access" as IAM
component "Asset Lifecycle" as AssetLifecycle
component "Maintenance & Warranty" as Maintenance
component "Reporting & Insights" as Reporting
component "AI Orchestration" as AIOrch
component "Audit & Compliance" as Audit
database "PostgreSQL\n(System of Record)" as DB
component "Async Workers / Event Bus" as Workers
cloud "AI Providers\n(LLM / OCR / Predictive)" as AIProviders

User --> Frontend : UI actions
Frontend --> API : HTTPS API calls

API --> IAM : authz/authn
API --> AssetLifecycle : lifecycle commands
API --> Maintenance : maintenance commands
API --> Reporting : reporting queries
API --> AIOrch : AI-assisted requests
API --> Audit : append audit events

IAM --> DB
AssetLifecycle --> DB
Maintenance --> DB
Reporting --> DB
Audit --> DB
AIOrch --> Workers : async processing
Workers --> AIProviders : AI inference
AIOrch --> Audit : trace linkage

note right of AIOrch
AI outcomes are advisory.
Human approval gates apply
for high-impact actions.
end note
@enduml

